<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Bem-vindo • ZapConnect</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="icon" href="/img/favinco.png" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0D1222;
      --card: #161B30;
      --border: #2a3047;
      --text: #E8ECF7;
      --muted: #AAB0D9;
      --primary: #6C64EF;
      --primary-2: #5AC8FA;
      --success: #22C55E;
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Inter,system-ui,sans-serif;}
    body{
      margin:0;
      min-height:100vh;
      background:radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(108,100,239,.15), transparent 35%), radial-gradient(circle at 80% 0%, rgba(90,200,250,.2), transparent 30%), var(--bg);
      color:var(--text);
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      padding:20px;
    }
    .shell{
      width:100%;
      max-width:960px;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg,#181f3d,#0f1429);
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius:22px;
      padding:28px;
      box-shadow:0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,.45);
    }
    h1{margin:0;font-size:26px;}
    p.lead{color:var(--muted);margin:8px 0 20px;}
    .steps{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:14px;}
    .card{
      padding:18px;
      border-radius:16px;
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
    }
    .card::after{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      inset:0;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), transparent 40%);
      opacity:0;
      transition:.2s;
      pointer-events:none;
    }
    .card:hover::after{opacity:1;}
    .card h3{margin:10px 0 6px;font-size:16px;}
    .card p{margin:0;color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;line-height:1.4;}
    .pill{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:6px;
      padding:6px 10px;
      border-radius:999px;
      font-size:12px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border:1px solid var(--border);
      color:var(--text);
    }
    .btn{
      margin-top:12px;
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:8px;
      padding:10px 12px;
      border-radius:12px;
      border:1px solid transparent;
      cursor:pointer;
      color:#0b1225;
      font-weight:700;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--primary),var(--primary-2));
      box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(108,100,239,.35);
      text-decoration:none;
    }
    .btn.secondary{
      background:transparent;
      border-color:var(--border);
      color:var(--text);
      box-shadow:none;
    }
    .list{margin:10px 0 0;padding-left:18px;color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;}
    @media(max-width:640px){
      .shell{padding:22px;}
      h1{font-size:22px;}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="shell">
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:12px;">
      <span class="pill"><i class="fa-solid fa-rocket"></i> Primeiro passo</span>
    </div>
    <h1>Bem-vindo ao ZapConnect!</h1>
    <p class="lead">Completar estes 3 passos leva menos de 2 minutos e aumenta muito suas chances de ativar o produto.</p>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="card">
        <span class="pill" style="background:rgba(34,197,94,0.12);border-color:rgba(34,197,94,0.35);color:#a7f3d0"><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope-circle-check"></i> Passo 1</span>
        <h3>Confirme seu e-mail</h3>
        <p>Abra seu e-mail e clique no link de verificação para liberar todos os recursos.</p>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>Procure por "ZapConnect"</li>
          <li>Cheque a caixa de spam</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn secondary" href="https://mail.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i>
          Abrir Gmail
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <span class="pill" style="background:rgba(90,200,250,0.12);border-color:rgba(90,200,250,0.3);color:#cceeff"><i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen-button"></i> Passo 2</span>
        <h3>Conecte sua primeira sessão</h3>
        <p>Crie uma sessão e escaneie o QR code para atender pelo WhatsApp Web.</p>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>Use um número de WhatsApp ativo</li>
          <li>Mantenha o aparelho online na primeira conexão</li>
        </ul>
        <button class="btn" id="btn-go-panel" type="button">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-right-to-bracket"></i>
          Ir para o painel
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <span class="pill" style="background:rgba(108,100,239,0.12);border-color:rgba(108,100,239,0.35);color:#dcd6ff"><i class="fa-solid fa-magic"></i> Passo 3</span>
        <h3>Configure o prompt da IA</h3>
        <p>Defina tom de voz, saudações e limites. Isso melhora a qualidade das respostas.</p>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>Explique como sua empresa atende</li>
          <li>Inclua exemplos de boas respostas</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn secondary" href="/login">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-sliders"></i>
          Configurar depois
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
<script>
  const btn = document.getElementById("btn-go-panel");
  btn?.addEventListener("click", async () => {
    try {
      const res = await fetch("/auth/me", { credentials: "include" });
      if (res.ok) {
        window.location.href = "/painel";
      } else {
        window.location.href = "/login";
      }
    } catch {
      window.location.href = "/login";
    }
  });
</script>
</html>
